review.reviewBody: Delicious baked goodies like bird's nest cookies
Disappointed. For the amount of $$ spent I expected a whole panini and bigger desserts. The pictures are very misleading.  My cookie certainly wasnt 4inches and it was hard as a rock.
The chicken pot pie was great but I didn't know it had corn which I'm allergic too so I couldn'  enjoy it :(

We are from Atlanta, GA, USA and I wish we had a bakery like this near us! Delicious pot pies, and when they didn't have enough to fulfill our whole order they gave us other entrees and pumpkin cookies as compensation (which were amazing!) Thank you!
Literally the only place I can get a gluten free wrap 10/10 <3
